---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Wassim Soltani</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        Full-Stack Software Engineer | AI/ML Integration Specialist | Cloud & Edge Computing Expert
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
        <a 
          href="/connect" 
          class="relative bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 animate-glow"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://github.com/wSoltani" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer" 
          class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
          </svg>
          View GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Summary -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">About Me</h2>
        <a href="/ai-chat" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all text-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
          </svg>
          Ask AI
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl mb-6">
        I'm a Software Engineer who transforms complex challenges into elegant, scalable solutions. My technical expertise spans AI integration (AWS Bedrock, Cloudflare AI), full-stack development (React, TypeScript, Java, Spring Boot), and cloud/edge computing—all delivered with a focus on performance, scalability, and exceptional user experience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">
        As the founder of Blueblood, I've led the development of AI-powered applications that streamline workflows and enhance productivity. My work includes creating <a href="https://qmims.vercel.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">qmims</a> (my first open-source contribution), developing sophisticated browser extensions for data automation, and building serverless AI solutions like <a href="https://quickplan.blueblood.tech/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Quickplan</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <a href="/skills" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-lg">View my full skillset →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Projects Summary -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-t-md">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Featured Projects</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Quickplan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">AI-powered web application for processing meeting notes</p>
        <a href="https://quickplan.blueblood.tech/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View Project →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">qmims <span class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-normal">(open-source)</span></h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">AI-powered CLI tool for README generation and editing</p>
        <a href="https://qmims.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View Project →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/projects" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-lg">View all projects →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience Summary -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Professional Experience</h2>
        <a href="/ai-chat" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all text-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
          </svg>
          Ask AI
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Software Engineer | Vantage Labs LLC</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">April 2022 – Present</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Developing AI-driven educational tools, browser extensions, and full-stack applications as a full-time team member. Operating through my company, Blueblood.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Lead Full-stack Developer/Engineer | Almaviva S.p.A</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">September 2019 – March 2022</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Led enterprise software development initiatives, delivering high-performance applications with a focus on scalability and user experience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
        <a href="/experience" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-lg">View detailed experience →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-b-md">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Education</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Master's Degree in Computer Science</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Tek-Up University | 2019 - 2022</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Specialized in Software Engineering and Information Systems. Focused on advanced software development methodologies, distributed systems, and enterprise architecture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science Applied to Business Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Tunisia Private School (ULT) | 2016 - 2019</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Core computer science curriculum including algorithms, data structures, software engineering principles, and practical programming skills applied to business management.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Assistant CTA -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 rounded-lg my-8 relative" style="background-image: url('/hero.webp'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-900">Have Questions?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-800 mb-6">
          Chat with my AI assistant to learn more about my experience, skills, and projects. It can answer questions about my work, provide details about specific technologies I've used, and help you navigate my portfolio.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/ai-chat" 
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
          </svg>
          Chat with AI Assistant
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md w-full max-w-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="flex mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                AI
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-3 rounded-lg max-w-[80%]">
              <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
                Hello! I'm Wassim's assistant. How can I help you learn more about his experience and skills?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-end mb-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-3 rounded-lg max-w-[80%] ml-3">
              <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
                What projects has Wassim worked on?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                AI
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-3 rounded-lg max-w-[80%]">
              <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm">
                Wassim has worked on several notable projects including Quickplan, qmims, and an AI-Enhanced E-commerce Platform. Would you like to know more about any of these?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect CTA -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        I'm always interested in hearing about new projects and opportunities. Whether you have a question or just want to say hi, I'll try my best to get back to you!
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/connect" 
        class="relative bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 text-lg animate-glow"
      >
        Connect With Me
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes glow {
    0% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
    }
    70% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0);
    }
    100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(37, 99, 235, 0);
    }
  }

  .animate-glow {
    animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
